name: CongressJBot
tagline: A Java reddit bot for posting the activities of congress to reddit. It's a Java duplicate of congressbot.
body:
### Welcome to the CongressJBot information page!

/r/FuturistParty's FuturistBot is powered by CongressJBot!

There's not much here right now, but you can check out the project [here](https://github.com/techietotoro/CongressJBot).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
